snippet.title: High Rise Trailer
snippet.description:
High Rise is a innovative take on the match 3 genre. A relaxed casual puzzle experience. Match colourful cubes and watch them merge, grow and your 3D puzzle cityscape rise.

Available for free for Android and iOS.
iOS https://apps.apple.com/app/id1479215827
Android https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SMPL.HighRise
